item.title: CVE-2022-1685|2024-08-03T00:10:03.847Z -- unknown -- five%20minute%20webshop
item.description: The Five Minute Webshop WordPress plugin through 1.3.2 does not properly validate and sanitise the orderby parameter before using it in a SQL statement via the Manage Products admin page, leading to an SQL Injection

item.title: CVE-2022-1686|2024-08-03T00:10:03.913Z -- unknown -- five%20minute%20webshop
